{"id":26532,"date":"2024-02-21T11:59:47","date_gmt":"2021-10-21T06:29:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=26532"},"modified":"2022-08-30T14:25:48","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T08:55:48","slug":"double-sided-sofa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/double-sided-sofa\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Double-Sided Sofa Design Ideas For Your Modern Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Add some extra seating space to your home with luxurious double-sided sofa designs<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A sofa is undoubtedly one of the most essential pieces of furniture in your living room. It is the place where you end up spending the longest periods in the common area \u2014 be it watching your favourite show with your kids, hosting a FIFA night for your friends or reading your favourite novel while snuggling under a blanket after a long day of work. A comfortable sofa is crucial to alleviate the cosiness quotient of your living room. You might have come across many designer sofas, from traditional designs to modern ones, but today we bring to you unique and voguish double-sided sofa designs that will give a stylish edge to your living room while adding a lot of seating space in your living area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Double-Sided Modular Sofa Design To Elevate The Look And Functionality Of Your Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a comfortable seating arrangement where you can chill and vibe with the entire family? This double-sided modular sofa is the best option for you. But vibing together has its pros and cons. There might be a time when your kids want to watch their favourite show, but you want to sit and enjoy the sunset with a cup of tea. Now you can enjoy your own time while being with your entire family. Place this double-sided modular sofa in your living room, one side facing the TV unit and the other facing the window. Next time, enjoy your favourite book while gazing at the evening sky while your kids enjoy their gaming night or their favourite show.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112531\/a-double-sided-sofa-design-to-elevate-the-look-and-functionality-of-your-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"A double sided sofa sofa design to elevate the look and functionality of your living room\" class=\"wp-image-26534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112531\/a-double-sided-sofa-design-to-elevate-the-look-and-functionality-of-your-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112531\/a-double-sided-sofa-design-to-elevate-the-look-and-functionality-of-your-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112531\/a-double-sided-sofa-design-to-elevate-the-look-and-functionality-of-your-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112531\/a-double-sided-sofa-design-to-elevate-the-look-and-functionality-of-your-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A double-sided modular sofa that goes exceptionally well with your modern interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Double-Sided Chesterfield Sofa To Enhance The Look of Your Industrial-Style Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A chesterfield sofa is a timeless piece of furniture. It brings an old-world charm to the entire room. The leather upholstery and the unique shine is all that you need to jazz up your space. Now, what if we say we can help you take your retro home interiors a notch higher? We present to you a double-sided chesterfield sofa. It enhances the look of your room and adds to the beauty while doubling your seating options. If you like an industrial-style living room with brick cladding walls, rustic furniture and track lights, this is it. The intricate design and golden panelling of the entertainment unit and sputnik light add to the grandeur of the space white the leather upholstered side table and an antique telephone piece adds a unique traditional vibe. This double-sided chesterfield sofa is sure to add to the style statement.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112910\/modern-double-sided-sofa-chesterfield-to-enhance-the-look-of-your-industrial-style-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Modern double sided sofa chesterfield to enhance the look of your industrial-style living room\" class=\"wp-image-26535\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112910\/modern-double-sided-sofa-chesterfield-to-enhance-the-look-of-your-industrial-style-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112910\/modern-double-sided-sofa-chesterfield-to-enhance-the-look-of-your-industrial-style-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112910\/modern-double-sided-sofa-chesterfield-to-enhance-the-look-of-your-industrial-style-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21112910\/modern-double-sided-sofa-chesterfield-to-enhance-the-look-of-your-industrial-style-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Take your style game a notch higher with a retro-style double-sided leather upholstered sofa\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Double-Sided Lounge Sofa for A Luxe Home Interior Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most convenient and comfortable double-sided sofa designs is the double-sided lounger sofa. You can use contrasting coloured double-sided sofa covers to add layers to your living room. You can also add a small work-from-home setup on one side of the sofa to take office calls or work on your presentations and when you need a small break between work, just come to the other side to enjoy an episode of \u2018Friends\u2019. This way, you can enjoy the best of both worlds in your living room. This sofa may take up a lot of space, so be mindful of using pastel walls, opt for large windows with sheer curtains and clean lines to make your room look spacious and airy. You can opt for a multifunctional entertainment unit as shown in the image. It comes with a closed cabinet, bookshelf and open shelves to organise your expensive showpieces, thus providing you with ample storage and display space. You can also have a small indoor garden for your personal meditation nook if space permits you to do so.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113147\/double-sided-modular-sofa-for-a-luxe-home-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Double sided modular sofa for a luxe home interior design to create a staycation vibe in your home \" class=\"wp-image-26536\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113147\/double-sided-modular-sofa-for-a-luxe-home-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113147\/double-sided-modular-sofa-for-a-luxe-home-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113147\/double-sided-modular-sofa-for-a-luxe-home-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113147\/double-sided-modular-sofa-for-a-luxe-home-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Create a staycation vibe in your home with this gorgeous double-sided lounge sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a living room that is lively and livable\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02171514\/living-room-lively-livable.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Double-Sided Sofa Bed To Add A Comforting Vibe To Your Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This double-sided sofa is ideal for a small living room. This double-sided sofa bed is compact, cute and excellent for you to snuggle in with your partner on a cosy evening. This is chic and comforting as well. Choose a vibrant colour for making this piece of furniture the focal point of your living room. Add two side low lying tables on either side of this double-sided sofa couch to keep your drinks and snacks. We have also added a home bar unit with two tall chairs to make your living area a happening space. Enjoy a couple of drinks with your friends and family while lounging on this couch in your comfortable clothes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113613\/double-sided-sofa-bed-to-add-a-comforting-vibe-to-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Double sided sofa bed to add a comforting vibe to your home\" class=\"wp-image-26537\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113613\/double-sided-sofa-bed-to-add-a-comforting-vibe-to-your-home.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113613\/double-sided-sofa-bed-to-add-a-comforting-vibe-to-your-home-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113613\/double-sided-sofa-bed-to-add-a-comforting-vibe-to-your-home-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21113613\/double-sided-sofa-bed-to-add-a-comforting-vibe-to-your-home-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Smart double-sided sofa bed to add additional seating space in your compact living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Simple Low-Lying Double-Sided Sofa For A Chic Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This low-lying double-sided sofa is excellent for socialising with friends and family. It is incredibly comfortable and adds a luxurious vibe to your home. The wooden frame adds to the aesthetics of the space. The wainscoting wall makes the area extremely elegant and stylish. At the same time, the dining table, side cabinet and book cabinet with shelves and drawers elevate the room\u2019s functionality and make it look highly decorous. You can also add a floor rug for an additional cosy and comforting vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21115100\/a-simple-low-lying-double-sided-sofa-for-a-chic-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"A simple low-lying double-sided sofa for a chic living room\" class=\"wp-image-26538\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21115100\/a-simple-low-lying-double-sided-sofa-for-a-chic-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21115100\/a-simple-low-lying-double-sided-sofa-for-a-chic-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21115100\/a-simple-low-lying-double-sided-sofa-for-a-chic-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/21115100\/a-simple-low-lying-double-sided-sofa-for-a-chic-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A low-lying double-sided sofa with a wooden frame to add some warmth to your interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you excited to incorporate these cuties in your living room but a little worried about the perfect home interiors 